@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Current USD rates
GET {{baseUrl}}/rates?currency=USD
Accept: application/json

### Current EUR rates
GET {{baseUrl}}/rates?currency=EUR
Accept: application/json

### Convert USD to EUR
GET {{baseUrl}}/convert?from=USD&to=EUR&amount=100
Accept: application/json

### Convert USD to RUB
GET {{baseUrl}}/convert?from=USD&to=RUB&amount=100
Accept: application/json

### Recent USD history
# Requires DATABASE_URL and a running PostgreSQL instance.
GET {{baseUrl}}/rates/history?currency=USD&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### USD history by date
# Date-only "to" includes the entire specified day.
GET {{baseUrl}}/rates/history/by-date?currency=USD&from=2026-06-01&to=2026-06-06&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics
Accept: text/plain

### Pprof index
GET {{baseUrl}}/debug/pprof/

### Validation error example
GET {{baseUrl}}/rates?currency=USDT
Accept: application/json

### Method not allowed example
POST {{baseUrl}}/rates?currency=USD
Accept: application/json
